data.description: Welcome to Windsor Park Townhomes! This nicely updated 2 bedroom 1 ½ bath END UNIT is located in the private community of Windsor Park off of Palm Bay Road. Brand new roof to be installed by HOA by end of August! This town home offers 2 large bedrooms upstairs, an updated kitchen with soft closing cabinets, stainless steel appliances, laundry in kitchen, 2019 AC, 2022 water heater, private porch, and a large fenced in back yard. The HOA covers general maintenance, and your water bill is included! Close to grocery stores, restaurants, Harris Corp, Northrop Grumman, and less than 20 minutes from the beach!
